timeline.message: Fix cipher suite with okhttp3.11.0 and refine restclient with 1.7.1

timeline.bodyText: are there tests that should be added that correspond with these 5 string changes?
timeline.author: joshfree

replies.bodyText: The is actually what okhttp adds cipher suite. I don't know how to add unit test with special dependency version (okhttp 3.11.0). And I have test with it successfully for whole profile.
